  <p><strong>Every Student Should Have a Safe Learning Environment</strong></p>
  <p> How many students in your school or community have been harmed by bullying?<br />
   Be a leader by showing that you care. You can take action with this guide designed for students and educators to plan bullying prevention events in their school or community.<br />
